.	root,entry	Repo root. Three pre-built .so files here (connect6s_cpp, connect6s_heuristic_cpp, connect6s_mcts_cpp). Must run 'bash scripts/build_heuristic.sh' after any C++ edit — stale .so silently shadows Python changes. bot.py + main.py are entry points.
connect6s	core,python	Core Python package. game.py auto-loads C++ .so if present. mcts.py is overridden by mcts_cpp.so at runtime — edits to mcts.py silently ignored unless .so absent. heuristic_agent.py wraps C++ alpha-beta with same interface as MCTS.
bot.py	bot,arena	Arena bot. SSE stream. Time-budget mode (BOT_SIMS=0): 10-30% remaining clock per move, capped 20s (5s heuristic). BOT_HEURISTIC=1 routes to C++ alpha-beta. Reads .env for BOT_API_KEY/ARENA_URL/ROOM_ID.
connect6s/heuristic_cpp.cpp	heuristic,cpp,pitfall,hot	HOT PATH. C++ alpha-beta search + incremental eval. Key pitfalls: (1) mixed-window trap L204: n_opp>0 → score=0 for us — center capture gets atk≈0 because our piece flanked by opp pieces makes all shared windows mixed; endpoint capture gets atk=520 from clean own-window. IDA prefers endpoint by 372pts at every depth. (2) cell_value() measures new-piece gain ONLY — for captures use actual eval diff b.score[opp]-after.score[opp], not cell_value(). (3) gen_moves score does NOT determine root move — search_at_depth picks by minimax value; huge gen_moves bonus is irrelevant for root selection. (4) find_line_split threshold must be >=4, NOT >=3 — run>=3 fires during our offense → game1 regression. (5) Pipeline order: VCF → opp-VCF(capture-first) → find_block_upgrade → find_line_split → IDA. Rebuild after edit: bash scripts/build_heuristic.sh.
connect6s/mcts_cpp.cpp	mcts,cpp	C++ MCTS: PUCT selection, virtual loss, Zobrist TT, batched leaf eval. Compiles to connect6s_mcts_cpp.so. Edits to mcts.py are dead unless .so removed.
connect6s/game.cpp	game,cpp	C++ GameState + game.hpp. Compiles to connect6s_cpp.so. Zobrist hash, strong-piece logic, action encoding (450 = 225 reg + 225 strong). Blast radius: any change breaks all three .so files indirectly via game.hpp.
scripts	scripts,ops	Key scripts: build_heuristic.sh (must run after C++ edits), play.sh (arena bot), train_forever.sh/train_large.sh (tmux), health_check.sh.
models	models,ml	Only best.pt tracked by git (iter_*.pt excluded). Sandbox: repo ≤ 192 MiB. Submit = replace best.pt. BOT_HEURISTIC=1 ignores this entirely.
connect6s/network.py	network,ml	PolicyValueNet: stem Conv → N ResBlocks → policy(450 logits) + value(tanh). Small: 6b/128ch. Large: 8b/192ch. Obs: (6,15,15). Action 450.
connect6s/config.py	config	Production config: small net (6b/128ch), 6 workers. config_large.py subclasses for 8b/192ch, 3 workers, models/best_large.pt.
